e your current version of the add-on.\r\n1. Download the latest version of the add-on from our [support site](https://support.learndash.com/article-categories/free/).\r\n1. Upload the zipped file via PLUGINS > ADD NEW, or to wp-content/plugins.\r\n1. Activate the add-on plugin via the PLUGINS menu.\r\n\r\n\";s:7:\"content\";s:657:\"<p>If the auto-update is not working, verify that you have a valid LearnDash LMS license via LEARNDASH LMS &gt; SETTINGS &gt; LMS LICENSE. </p>\n<p>Alternatively, you always have the option to update manually. Please note, a full backup of your site is always recommended prior to updating. </p>\n<ol>\n<li>Deactivate and delete your current version of the add-on.</li>\n<li>Download the latest version of the add-on from our <a href=\"https://support.learndash.com/article-categories/free/\">support site</a>.</li>\n<li>Upload the zipped file via PLUGINS &gt; ADD NEW, or to wp-content/plugins.</li>\n<li>Activate the add-on plugin via the PLUGINS menu.</li>\n</ol>\";}s:9:\"changelog\";a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Changelog\";s:11:\"content_raw\";s:562:\"= 1.3.0 =\r\n* Added new Stripe checkout integration button\r\n* Added `receipt_email` prop to Stripe API Charge object\r\n* Added endpoint secret setting\r\n* Added webhook URL readonly setting\r\n* Added new checkout fields toggle scripts\r\n* Updated Stripe PHP SDK\r\n* Updated the order of PK and SK fields on settings page\r\n* Updated Stripe plan to comply with latest Stripe API\r\n* Updated language files\r\n* Removed new checkout code from legacy checkout class\r\n* Fixed Undefined Index error\r\n\r\nView the full changelog [here](https://www.learndash.com/add-on/stripe/).\r\n\";s:7:\"content\";s:668:\"<h4>1.3.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added new Stripe checkout integration button</li>\n<li>Added <code>receipt_email</code> prop to Stripe API Charge object</li>\n<li>Added endpoint secret setting</li>\n<li>Added webhook URL readonly setting</li>\n<li>Added new checkout fields toggle scripts</li>\n<li>Up